---
import PageShell from '../../components/PageShell.astro';
import CTABox from '../../components/CTABox.astro';
import ComparisonTable from '../../components/ComparisonTable.astro';

const tocItems = [
  { id: 'overview', text: 'Overview', level: 2 },
  { id: 'coverage-comparison', text: 'Coverage Comparison', level: 2 },
  { id: 'pricing', text: 'Pricing', level: 2 },
  { id: 'network-and-claims', text: 'Network and Claims', level: 2 },
  { id: 'who-should-choose', text: 'Who Should Choose Which', level: 2 },
  { id: 'verdict', text: 'Our Verdict', level: 2 },
];

const relatedLinks = [
  { title: 'Cigna Global Review', href: '/providers/cigna-global' },
  { title: 'Allianz Care Review', href: '/providers/allianz-care' },
  { title: 'Best Expat Insurance', href: '/best/expat-health-insurance' },
  { title: 'Spain Insurance Guide', href: '/countries/spain/insurance' },
  { title: 'France Insurance Guide', href: '/countries/france/insurance' },
];

const coverageColumns = [
  { key: 'feature', header: 'Feature' },
  { key: 'cigna', header: 'Cigna Global' },
  { key: 'allianz', header: 'Allianz Care' },
];

const coverageRows = [
  { feature: 'Inpatient Care', cigna: true, allianz: true },
  { feature: 'Outpatient Care', cigna: true, allianz: true },
  { feature: 'Mental Health', cigna: true, allianz: true },
  { feature: 'Maternity', cigna: 'Optional', allianz: 'Optional' },
  { feature: 'Dental', cigna: 'Optional', allianz: 'Optional' },
  { feature: 'Vision', cigna: 'Optional', allianz: 'Limited' },
  { feature: 'Wellness Programs', cigna: true, allianz: true },
  { feature: 'Medical Evacuation', cigna: true, allianz: true },
  { feature: 'US Coverage', cigna: 'Add-on', allianz: 'Add-on' },
];

const pricingColumns = [
  { key: 'profile', header: 'Profile' },
  { key: 'cigna', header: 'Cigna Global' },
  { key: 'allianz', header: 'Allianz Care' },
];

const pricingRows = [
  { profile: 'Single, Age 30', cigna: '$140-180/mo', allianz: '$120-160/mo' },
  { profile: 'Single, Age 45', cigna: '$220-280/mo', allianz: '$190-250/mo' },
  { profile: 'Couple, Age 35', cigna: '$280-360/mo', allianz: '$240-320/mo' },
  { profile: 'Family of 4', cigna: '$450-600/mo', allianz: '$400-550/mo' },
];
---

<PageShell
  title="Cigna Global vs Allianz Care"
  description="Compare Cigna Global and Allianz Care side by side. See coverage, pricing, and which plan may be right for you."
  headline="Cigna Global vs Allianz Care: Which Is Right for You?"
  subheadline="Both are popular choices for expat health insurance. Here's how they compare on coverage, price, and service."
  tocItems={tocItems}
  relatedLinks={relatedLinks}
  ctaButtonText="Get Quotes from Both"
  ctaButtonHref="/best/expat-health-insurance"
>
  <h2 id="overview">Overview</h2>
  <p>
    Cigna Global and Allianz Care are two of the most well-known international health insurance providers. Both offer comprehensive coverage for expats living abroad, but they have different strengths.
  </p>

  <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6 my-8">
    <div class="bg-neutral-50 border border-neutral-200 rounded-lg p-6">
      <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-neutral-900 mb-3">Cigna Global</h3>
      <ul class="space-y-2 text-neutral-600">
        <li>Large global hospital network</li>
        <li>Strong customer service reputation</li>
        <li>Good family and maternity options</li>
        <li>Higher premiums in some cases</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
    <div class="bg-neutral-50 border border-neutral-200 rounded-lg p-6">
      <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-neutral-900 mb-3">Allianz Care</h3>
      <ul class="space-y-2 text-neutral-600">
        <li>Flexible plan customization</li>
        <li>Competitive pricing</li>
        <li>Strong mental health coverage</li>
        <li>Good for frequent movers</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </div>

  <CTABox
    title="Compare Both Providers"
    description="Get quotes from Cigna Global and Allianz Care for your situation."
    buttonText="Get Free Quotes"
    buttonHref="/best/expat-health-insurance"
    variant="highlight"
  />

  <h2 id="coverage-comparison">Coverage Comparison</h2>
  <p>
    Both plans cover the essentials you need as an expat. The main differences are in optional add-ons and the depth of certain benefits.
  </p>

  <div class="my-8 border border-neutral-200 rounded-lg overflow-hidden">
    <ComparisonTable columns={coverageColumns} rows={coverageRows} />
  </div>

  <p>
    <strong>Key differences:</strong>
  </p>
  <ul>
    <li>Cigna Global tends to have broader vision coverage as an add-on</li>
    <li>Allianz Care includes more mental health benefits in base plans</li>
    <li>Both offer maternity as optional coverage with waiting periods</li>
  </ul>

  <h2 id="pricing">Pricing</h2>
  <p>
    Prices depend on your age, coverage level, deductible choice, and where you live. Here are estimated monthly premiums for common profiles. Your actual quote may differ.
  </p>

  <div class="my-8 border border-neutral-200 rounded-lg overflow-hidden">
    <ComparisonTable columns={pricingColumns} rows={pricingRows} />
  </div>

  <p>
    <strong>Notes on pricing:</strong>
  </p>
  <ul>
    <li>Allianz Care is often 10-15% less expensive for similar coverage</li>
    <li>Adding US coverage increases premiums significantly for both</li>
    <li>Higher deductibles can reduce premiums by 20-30%</li>
  </ul>

  <CTABox
    title="Get Your Actual Price"
    description="Estimates vary. See what you'd actually pay based on your details."
    buttonText="Get a Quote"
    buttonHref="/best/expat-health-insurance"
  />

  <h2 id="network-and-claims">Network and Claims</h2>

  <h3>Provider Networks</h3>
  <p>
    <strong>Cigna Global</strong> has a larger direct-billing network with over 1.5 million providers worldwide. This means you can often see a doctor without paying upfront.
  </p>
  <p>
    <strong>Allianz Care</strong> has a smaller direct-billing network but still covers major hospitals in most countries. You may need to pay and file for reimbursement more often.
  </p>

  <h3>Claims Process</h3>
  <p>
    Both providers offer online claims submission and mobile apps. Cigna Global's claims portal is generally rated as more user-friendly. Allianz Care claims can sometimes take longer to process.
  </p>

  <h3>Customer Service</h3>
  <p>
    Cigna Global offers 24/7 support in multiple languages. Allianz Care also provides multilingual support but availability may vary by region.
  </p>

  <h2 id="who-should-choose">Who Should Choose Which</h2>

  <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6 my-8">
    <div class="bg-primary-50 border border-primary-200 rounded-lg p-6">
      <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-neutral-900 mb-3">Choose Cigna Global If:</h3>
      <ul class="space-y-2 text-neutral-600">
        <li>You want the largest provider network</li>
        <li>You're a family with children</li>
        <li>You prefer direct billing over reimbursement</li>
        <li>Customer service quality is a priority</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
    <div class="bg-neutral-50 border border-neutral-200 rounded-lg p-6">
      <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-neutral-900 mb-3">Choose Allianz Care If:</h3>
      <ul class="space-y-2 text-neutral-600">
        <li>You want to save on premiums</li>
        <li>You move between countries frequently</li>
        <li>Mental health coverage is important to you</li>
        <li>You prefer flexible plan options</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </div>

  <h2 id="verdict">Our Verdict</h2>
  <p>
    Both Cigna Global and Allianz Care are solid choices for expat health insurance. There's no clear "winner" because the right choice depends on your priorities.
  </p>
  <p>
    <strong>Cigna Global</strong> may be a better fit if you value a large network, seamless direct billing, and don't mind paying a bit more for those conveniences.
  </p>
  <p>
    <strong>Allianz Care</strong> may suit you better if you're budget-conscious, value flexibility, or prioritize mental health coverage.
  </p>
  <p>
    We recommend getting quotes from both providers to see actual pricing for your situation. The difference in premiums might influence your decision.
  </p>

  <CTABox
    title="Ready to Decide?"
    description="Compare quotes from both providers based on your specific needs."
    buttonText="Compare Plans Now"
    buttonHref="/best/expat-health-insurance"
    variant="highlight"
  />

  <div class="bg-neutral-50 border border-neutral-200 rounded-lg p-6 mt-8">
    <p class="text-sm text-neutral-600">
      <strong>Disclaimer:</strong> This comparison is for informational purposes only. Prices, coverage, and plan details change. We are not insurance brokers. Verify all information with the providers before purchasing.
    </p>
  </div>
</PageShell>
